reviewText: Don't bother. These three movies are nothing but a compilation of some of the episodes from the television show. If you've seen or own the series, then this is a total waste of money and time.
This is great unless you all ready own justice league seasons

Justice League Triple Feature is a great set to have for anyone who loves this genre of movies.  In this collections of videos the Justice League must work together to overcome a dangerous array of intersteller invaders and world conquering megalomaniacs.  When the Thanagarians visit Earth, Hawkgirl is forced to choose between loyalty to her people and love for her friends on her adopted planet Earth.  The galaxy's ultimate crime-fighting strike squad, the Justice League, continues its on-going battle against enemies on the Earth and beyond.  In "Paradise Lost," sorcerer Felix Faust turns Wonder Woman's Amazon sisters to statues of stone!  Then, Superman is captured by the warlord Mongul and plunged into a gladiator-style fight to the finish.  This is a great set of movies and I would definitely recommend it to others.

Thank you for reading my review.
